Competition Carbon Z06X Ducktail spoiler! 

Finished with the design, renders, and now ready for CNC mold. 

It’s like a C8 Z06 low spoiler but with 20mm taller gourmet flaps. 

Will be made entirely out of Autoclave Carbon 2x2 weaves. 

Mounting will be 4 bolts in stock C8 spoiler plus 3m tape. 

Can possibly get away with just tape for the no OEM spoiler C8. 

MSRP will be 1499 plus 150 for shipping. 

Groupbuy preorder will be 20% off. 

ETA for delivery is 10 weeks. 

Preorder will be up on our Competition Carbon website tonight… do not buy from anyone else because those are scammers
